<dgm:dataModel xmlns:dgm="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/diagram" xmlns:a="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/main"><dgm:ptLst><dgm:pt modelId="{A32E232A-99A2-41A4-A401-4F2D3CF3856F}" type="doc"><dgm:prSet loTypeId="urn:microsoft.com/office/officeart/2005/8/layout/architecture" loCatId="list" qsTypeId="urn:microsoft.com/office/officeart/2005/8/quickstyle/simple1" qsCatId="simple" csTypeId="urn:microsoft.com/office/officeart/2005/8/colors/accent1_2" csCatId="accent1" phldr="1"/><dgm:spPr/><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN"/></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{F8F0C4F4-5C32-4991-97C2-325091505A3D}"><dgm:prSet phldrT="[Text]" phldr="0"/><dgm:spPr><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="303656"/></a:solidFill></dgm:spPr><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr algn="l"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>-Code sage supports many </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US"/><a:t>regional languages.</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr algn="l"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>-Creates personalized learning path for each individual.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr algn="l"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>-Has number of questions of each level to cater every individual.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr algn="l"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" dirty="0"/><a:t>-Code sage is integrated with GitHub which allows users to directly upload their projects.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr algn="l"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" dirty="0"/><a:t>-It allows users to undergo mock interviews which are tailored based on the company they are targeting.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr algn="l"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" dirty="0"/><a:t>-It has interactive quizzes and leaderboards which maintains competitiveness in the community.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr algn="l"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-IN" dirty="0"/><a:t>-It suggests hackathons and certification courses based on users need and accessibility.</a:t></a:r></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{F6B21E46-D5FD-421C-8223-C1ADC1825A4A}" type="parTrans" cxnId="{899D46AD-E2CF-43B8-A4A9-FB9CF004563D}"><dgm:prSet/><dgm:spPr/><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN"/></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{F964C8BA-1579-45C8-B13D-3F88B3DD905D}" type="sibTrans" cxnId="{899D46AD-E2CF-43B8-A4A9-FB9CF004563D}"><dgm:prSet/><dgm:spPr/><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN"/></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{A497DE01-5250-41F1-BE34-F02DD4693476}"><dgm:prSet phldrT="[Text]" phldr="0"/><dgm:spPr><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="1C2033"/></a:solidFill></dgm:spPr><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr algn="l"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>Code sage is a web-application which provides users with an AI mentor with personalized learning. It also suggests various problems(from easy to extreme) to the users which helps them to practically implement their logic.</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN" dirty="0"/></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{C5F45EEF-D384-44F1-96E3-E6CBE45780F3}" type="parTrans" cxnId="{6FE1B2FD-6739-464C-B03E-8784AED77C79}"><dgm:prSet/><dgm:spPr/><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN"/></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{DDC58D4D-382F-4A64-9DE3-87721DF71C1D}" type="sibTrans" cxnId="{6FE1B2FD-6739-464C-B03E-8784AED77C79}"><dgm:prSet/><dgm:spPr/><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN"/></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{A318CBEA-3DCB-4483-AB8D-D10905F2E75E}"><dgm:prSet phldrT="[Text]" phldr="0"/><dgm:spPr><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="1C2033"/></a:solidFill></dgm:spPr><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr algn="r"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>Users get a personalized learning path which cater to their needs in their regional language which helps them to understand fundamentals better. Problem solving using the questions suggested by code sage improves their practical knowledge and helps them to crack professional interviews.</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN" dirty="0"/></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{E973A424-7B3F-41EB-924A-1648148548B3}" type="parTrans" cxnId="{4580974D-BE40-43CA-9AFD-F9B18DC0481B}"><dgm:prSet/><dgm:spPr/><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN"/></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{1EE3584C-450D-4E2B-9A1F-12A713B3942E}" type="sibTrans" cxnId="{4580974D-BE40-43CA-9AFD-F9B18DC0481B}"><dgm:prSet/><dgm:spPr/><dgm:t><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN"/></a:p></dgm:t></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{5EB45712-AFA4-4C8A-B611-B199BCD18548}" type="pres"><dgm:prSet presAssocID="{A32E232A-99A2-41A4-A401-4F2D3CF3856F}" presName="Name0" presStyleCnt="0"><dgm:presLayoutVars><dgm:chPref val="1"/><dgm:dir/><dgm:animOne val="branch"/><dgm:animLvl val="lvl"/><dgm:resizeHandles/></dgm:presLayoutVars></dgm:prSet><dgm:spPr/></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{6FCB018E-814E-426F-B56C-DCE7E68E4965}" type="pres"><dgm:prSet presAssocID="{F8F0C4F4-5C32-4991-97C2-325091505A3D}" presName="vertOne" presStyleCnt="0"/><dgm:spPr/></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{D1E09052-DAB0-4881-9566-002155517CC5}" type="pres"><dgm:prSet presAssocID="{F8F0C4F4-5C32-4991-97C2-325091505A3D}" presName="txOne" presStyleLbl="node0" presStyleIdx="0" presStyleCnt="1" custLinFactNeighborX="5" custLinFactNeighborY="-34926"><dgm:presLayoutVars><dgm:chPref val="3"/></dgm:presLayoutVars></dgm:prSet><dgm:spPr/></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{1F4A4547-8381-43B0-914A-F72E3081DA17}" type="pres"><dgm:prSet presAssocID="{F8F0C4F4-5C32-4991-97C2-325091505A3D}" presName="parTransOne" presStyleCnt="0"/><dgm:spPr/></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{0627B41D-FE36-48A3-98F5-C1EBB8EF2827}" type="pres"><dgm:prSet presAssocID="{F8F0C4F4-5C32-4991-97C2-325091505A3D}" presName="horzOne" presStyleCnt="0"/><dgm:spPr/></dgm:pt><dgm:pt modelId="{F14F912E-80A9-49CC-8C03-2C8FE59D19E5}" type="pres"><dgm:prSet presAssocID="{A497DE01-5250-41F1-BE34-F02DD4693476}" presName="vertTwo" pres